706885f-a.text:
160-184 Sterling Place, south side, west from Flatbush to Seventh Aves.,
showing also at the right foreground, the N.4. corner of Flatbush Ave. and
Sterling Place. In the background next to No. 160, is a new Christian
Science Church. w
